              "originalPosition": 110,
              "body": "More of a comment for the parent spec, but it seems a little odd we have a different identifier for the structure both in the media type and inside the TokenRequest (token_type) field? Was there a reason the media type is per token type?",
              "createdAt": "2023-02-10T15:10:59Z",
